The paper deals with the problem of signal parameter estimation and tracking, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT), control theory (cs.SY), and networking (cs.NI). The use of a state-space model and Bayesian analysis also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
